data.name: AppCodeNotFound
data.value: The applications unique numeric code was not found in the AppMaster table for the given AppId

data.name: DataSetTableNamesMismatchWithResultSet
data.value: A dataset was returned from the database and a collection of table names was provided but the count of the returned tables does not match what was supplied to the function.

data.name: DbCatalogMgrNotAvailable
data.value: The core catalog data structures were not available in the database so the catalog operations cannot be performed. Please ask DBA to check existences of CatalogTables, CatalogColumns, etc.

data.name: DbCommandBlockParameterReplacementFailed
data.value: The given parameter could not be found in the given dbCommandText and it needs to be replaced. This could indicate an invalid sql statement or the parameter deliminiters string does not include a required token.

data.name: DbParameterExistsInCollection
data.value: The given dbParameter already belongs to the dbParameter collection.

data.name: DbTableIndexNotFound
data.value: The database table was not defined with an index that had the required columns.

data.name: DbTablePrimaryKeyUndefined
data.value: The database table was not defined with a primary key and the operation required a table with a primary key or some other alternative index which was not supplied.

data.name: DbTablePrimaryKeyViolation
data.value: The record could not be inserted because the data caused a violation of the primary key constraint which requires all column values to be not null and together they must be unique.

data.name: EventLogFailoverFileWriteFailed
data.value: The primary target of the EventLog could not be written to and the failover file could also not be written to for the given critical prioirty event.

data.name: EventLogSourceCreateFailed
data.value: The given EventLog source does not exist and the program did not have privileges to create it. Please create it manually.

data.name: FileNotFound
data.value: The given found could not be found; check spelling of name or path.

data.name: FunctionNotImplementedForDbType
data.value: The function was not implemented for the current database type.

data.name: InvalidChangeToOracleDbCommandBlock
data.value: Once an Oracle DbCommandBlock has been formatted (by accessing the DbCommandBlock property, it cannot have any new commands added to it.

data.name: InvalidFormatStringDynamicSQL
data.value: The format string used to generate a dynamic sql command did not have the proper parameters

data.name: InvalidParameterValue
data.value: The value of the parameter is not valid

data.name: MissingRequiredConfigurationValue
data.value: The was not configuration value defined for the given key which required a value

data.name: NullOrEmptyParameter
data.value: A parameter was passed with a null or empty value.

data.name: TaskQueueCodeNotFoundAtCompletion
data.value: The given TaskQueueCode was not by the taskCompletion delegate. This is an internal error with the TaskProcessingEngine which indicates that a task that just completed was not recorded as being started.

data.name: TasksInProcessCounterUnderFlow
data.value: The tasksInProcess counter cannot be less than 0. This is an internal error in the TaskProcessingEngine.

data.name: UnknownException
data.value: Unexpected error event occurred.

data.name: UnsupportedDbType
data.value: The database type given is not yet supported.
